platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.ta.k: Hide and seek in the Wild West

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: El Hijo blends charm and easygoing puzzle challenges into an artfully told tale of a child in search of his mother. When we’re not admiring its enchanting landscapes, we’re smiling at the way we have to think like a mischievous 6-year-old to sneak past monks and outlaws. Somewhere between dashing behind curtains and using moving bison for cover, it became one of our favorite stealth games.
